7[5] "Product Information. Rexulti (brexpiprazole)." Otsuka American Pharmaceuticals Inc, Rockville, MD.[6] "Product Information. Alunbrig (brigatinib)." Ariad Pharmaceuticals Inc, Cambridge, MA.', 1767369485);
