id, More', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Velpatasvir, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/4713/', '[1] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] Caraco Y, Sheller J, Wood AJ "Pharmacogenetic determinants of codeine induction by rifampin: the impact on codeine''s respiratory, psychomotor and miotic effects." J Pharmacol Exp Ther 281 (1997): 330-6[4] "Product Information. Acetaminophen-Codeine Phosphate (acetaminophen-codeine)." Qualitest Pharmaceuticals Inc, Huntsville, ON.[5] "Product Information. Codeine Sulfate (codeine)." Lannett Company Inc, Philadelphia, PA.[6] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Canadian Product Information." O 0 (2015):[7] "Product Information. Tuzistra XR (chlorpheniramine-codeine)." Vernalis Pharmaceuticals Inc, Morristown, NJ.[8] "Product Information. Trikafta (elexacaftor/ivacaftor/tezacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.[9] "Product Information. Kalydeco (ivacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.[10] "Product Information. Orkambi (ivacaftor-lumacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.[11] "Product Information. Symdeko 4-Week (ivacaftor-tezacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.', 1767369485);
